flowchart TD
    A[Department] --> B[Permit Services Division]
    A --> E[Plan Review Division]
    A --> C[Field Inspections Division]
    A --> D[Code Enforcement Division]
    A --> RU[Records and Disclosure Unit]

    P[Property] --> PAR[Parcel]
    P --> ADR[Address]

    APP[Permit Application] -->|concerns| P
    APP -->|submitted by| APPL[Applicant]
    APP -->|for service| SVC[Public Service]
    APP -->|results in| PMT[Permit]
    APP --> PR[Plan Review]

    PMT -->|assigned to| C
    IR[Inspection Request] -->|for permit| PMT
    INSP[Inspection] -->|fulfills| IR
    INSP -->|inspected property| P
    INSP -->|performed by| INSPECTOR[Inspector]

    CASE[Violation Case] -->|related inspection| INSP
    CASE -->|related permit| PMT
    CASE -->|related property| P
    CASE --> NOV[Notice of Violation]
    CASE --> CA[Corrective Action]
    CASE --> APPEAL[Appeal]
    APPEAL --> HEARING[Hearing]
